text: Miloš Galin (born April 22, 1990) is a Bosnian-Herzegovinian footballer who plays for Sliema Wanderers in the Maltese Premier League. ==Club career== In January 2015, Galin signed a two-year contract with Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1 club CR Belouizdad.
